## SSh-Agent Forwarding:- To access private instance without storing pem file in public instance.
==========================

#Note:- After creating Public & Private instance follow below steps:-

# Open your terminal git bash & go to the pem file location & type below commands.

ssh-agent bash
ssh-add key.pem

# Now login to public instance
ssh -A ec2-user@publicIPaddress

# Now login to priate instance in same terminal
ssh ec2-user@privateIPaddress

